{"tid":2488202,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港女被判暴動縱火罪成，男友大叫「好快過，我哋出嚟結婚！」","createTime":"2021-04-14T05:32:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T05:47:28.000Z","uid":134071,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"1bb5b448dcbdec0ea4d2b2b306f2fb2142613cc3","tid":2488202,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T05:32:48.000Z","msg":"示威者前年9月在旺角警署外縱火堵路，事後一名年輕女咖啡師在現場附近一輛私家車上遇警截查，被指曾稱：「我頭先喺旺角警署出面X完差人，見到差人出嚟，驚咪走囉。」警方其後在她的背囊內搜出雷射筆。案件經審訊後，女咖啡師被裁定兩項縱火罪及一項暴動罪成，法官姚勳智今判她入獄四年半。<strong>散庭後，女被告男友大叫「好快過，我哋出嚟結婚！」被告含淚點頭回應；其父亦哭着大叫「政府無良呀！殘害青年呀！」</strong>旁聽支持者紛紛上前安慰二人，囚室內亦傳來被告的哭聲，庭內一片愁雲慘霧。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210414/PEMUB3VQGZDULPGDFIUITUCVOI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210414%2FPEMUB3VQGZDULPGDFIUITUCVOI%2F&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1Tvbkzvgmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=4bb11f6f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210414%2FPEMUB3VQGZDULPGDFIUITUCVOI%2F&h=8403ac0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210414/PEMUB3VQGZDULPGDFIUITUCVOI/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nw5A"},{"pid":"3519e19376a9f55d4f03c75b363de0bbbce85bcf","tid":2488202,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T05:33:08.000Z","msg":"手足有愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e0a11ecf2fc936e8a9783779b432d86191d275c","tid":2488202,"uid":31296,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T05:33:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d254ea17573df3e6c8b0a4c2c4fe71279ec80bb6","tid":2488202,"uid":7369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T05:33:37.000Z","msg":"頂住呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09a0bb30867a5798ddf4a94a98f2b85e17887cca","tid":2488202,"uid":91397,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy